detailsSection: Internet Explorer 5 content, including the Internet Explorer 5 Corporate Deployment Guide, the Internet Explorer Administration Kit, and the Microsoft Internet Explorer 5 Resource Kit, which includes everything the IT professional needs to deploy, manage, and support an enterprise installation of Internet Explorer 5

installInstructionSection:
1. The download is a pdf file. To start the download, click Download.
  2. If the File Download dialog box appears, do one of the following:
    • To start the download immediately, click Open.
    • To copy the download to your computer to view at a later time, click Save.
